            <textarea name="mensaje" rows="3" placeholder="Cu√©ntanos m√°s sobre tu pedido o evento..." class="w-full p-4 rounded-xl bg-background border-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all"></textarea>
